<h1 class="page-header">About Us</h1>
<p>Welcome to Jungle Rails, the ultimate destination for indoor plant enthusiasts and green thumbs alike. Nestled in the heart of the city, our little oasis is more than just a shop; it's a sanctuary for plant lovers to explore, learn, and connect with nature. Founded on the belief that every home deserves a touch of greenery, Green Haven offers a meticulously curated selection of indoor plants, from the lush foliage of exotic Monsteras to the delicate fronds of Ferns, and the hardy succulents for the more forgetful gardeners.</p>

<p>At Jungle Rails, we understand that bringing a new plant into your home is like adding a new member to your family. That's why we pride ourselves on not only providing the highest quality plants but also the knowledge and support you need to help them thrive. Our expert team is passionate about plants and eager to share their tips and tricks, whether you're a seasoned plant parent or just starting your journey. From choosing the right plant for your space to mastering the art of watering, we're here to guide you every step of the way.</p>

<p>But Jungle Rails is more than just a plant shop; it's a community. We host regular workshops, plant swaps, and events that bring together plant lovers from all walks of life. Whether you're looking to deepen your plant care knowledge, meet fellow enthusiasts, or just spend some time surrounded by greenery, Green Haven is the place to be. So come visit us and discover why our customers call Green Haven their happy place. Let's grow together!</p>
